@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Manage Account

|Patient|
start
:Open Account Menu;

|Frontend|
:Display Profile Information;

|Patient|
:Select Edit Profile;

|Frontend|
:Display Edit Profile Form;

|Patient|
:Update Account Information;
note right
- Name
- Email
- Phone Number
- Password
end note

:Click Save Changes;

|Frontend|
:Validate Input Data;

if (Input Valid?) then (Yes)

    |Backend|
    :Receive Updated Data;
    :Validate Email Uniqueness;

    if (Email Available?) then (Yes)

        :Update Account Data;
        :Save Changes to Database;

        |Frontend|
        :Display Update Success Message;
        :Refresh Profile Information;

        |Patient|
        :View Updated Profile;

        stop

    else (No)

        |Frontend|
        :Display Email Already Used Message;

        |Patient|
        :Correct Account Information;

    endif

else (No)

    |Frontend|
    :Display Validation Error;

    |Patient|
    :Correct Input Data;

endif

@enduml